      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>In Katana there are 2 ways to setup Stylized Looks:</p><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>A simple &quot;beginner&quot; Macro that has everything in it.</p></li><li><p>A more advanced manual option for the user to set everything up manually, with more control and daisy-chain options.</p></li></ol><p /><p>The beginner macro looks like this:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"1446\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178301/stylized-katana-macro.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530654&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1446&amp;height=1244\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178301/stylized-katana-macro.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530654&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1244\" data-width=\"1446\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178322\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"stylized-katana-macro.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178301\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"381bd243-c503-4551-af99-a226e808d9e7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178301/stylized-katana-macro.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530654&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1446&amp;height=1244 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178301/stylized-katana-macro.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530654&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1446&amp;height=1244 1x\"></span><p>In the macro, there are 3 nodes: Toon, Hatching, and Lines.</p><p>Outside the macro, there is also the StylizedControl node, which is connected to PxrSurface like this:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"402\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178301/stylized-katana-control.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530654&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=402&amp;height=249\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178301/stylized-katana-control.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530654&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"420\" data-width=\"676\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178325\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"stylized-katana-control.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178301\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"f5d43b42-987c-46e1-bb6f-6d8f1499f571\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178301/stylized-katana-control.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530654&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=676&amp;height=420 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178301/stylized-katana-control.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530654&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=402&amp;height=249 1x\"></span><p /><p>If the Stylized Looks macro isn't already in your scene, simply add it from scratch by hitting Tab in the Nodegraph, and it will appear in the menu like this:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"996\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178301/stylized-katana-macro-fromscratch.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530441&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=996&amp;height=510\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178301/stylized-katana-macro-fromscratch.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530441&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"510\" data-width=\"996\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178319\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"stylized-katana-macro-fromscratch.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178301\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"de2017c9-0f1e-4cef-8a24-8281e25c5056\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178301/stylized-katana-macro-fromscratch.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530441&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=996&amp;height=510 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178301/stylized-katana-macro-fromscratch.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530441&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=996&amp;height=510 1x\"></span><p /><p>Then, we add a shading node from the same menu:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"790\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178301/stylized-katana-shadingnode-fromscratch.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530441&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=790&amp;height=444\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178301/stylized-katana-shadingnode-fromscratch.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530441&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"444\" data-width=\"790\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178316\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"stylized-katana-shadingnode-fromscratch.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178301\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"96cea271-0148-47c8-9a83-04d6fab62c68\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178301/stylized-katana-shadingnode-fromscratch.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530441&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=790&amp;height=444 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178301/stylized-katana-shadingnode-fromscratch.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530441&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=790&amp;height=444 1x\"></span><p /><p>Then select <strong>PxrStylizedControl</strong>:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"470\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178301/stylized-katana-shadingnode-stylizedcontrol.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530440&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=470&amp;height=294\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178301/stylized-katana-shadingnode-stylizedcontrol.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530440&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"294\" data-width=\"470\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178313\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"stylized-katana-shadingnode-stylizedcontrol.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178301\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"469763cc-f150-4583-9b79-7b3b25b36039\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178301/stylized-katana-shadingnode-stylizedcontrol.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530440&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=470&amp;height=294 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178301/stylized-katana-shadingnode-stylizedcontrol.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531530440&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=470&amp;height=294 1x\"></span><p> and connect <strong>resultAOV</strong> to <strong>utilityPattern</strong> on <strong>PxrSurface</strong>.</p><p />"
    }
  },
